_sText:
de_crossfire is a port of the de_crossfire from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

DESCRIPTION:

A bomb-defuse map based high in the mountains.

Counter-Terrorist motivation: Today we are send on a special mission by the government. We think it has something to do about terrorists getting their hands on leaked information about reopening the abandoned factor. It was closed in the late 80s because some experiments went terribly wrong. We don't know what is happening there at the moment. All we were told is what is happening there needs to stay there.

Terrorist motivation: It is time. The leader won't say why we have to go on this specific assignment, but rumors are spread that the abandoned factory won't be abandoned for long. There are aliens there. They must be destroyed before the government or whoever use the aliens for the wrong reasons. You never know... Experiments, extracting poison, trying to make superhumans maybe... Dangerous business, that's for sure.

credits:

map and custom content by catfood

audio by hunsrus

Cruise (cs_cruise) - sea cruise ship map.

cs_cruise - is the conversion of a map cs_cruise from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

DESCRIPTION:

Hostage rescue mission

Pirates have boarded a luxury cruise ship during its voyage and have taken hostages. Security have managed to evacuate most of the passengers, but it's up to Seal team 6 to rescue those who remain at the mercy of the hijackers.

Special thanks to Mapcore.org and OrnateBaboon for playtesting and feedback.

This is an additional map for the mapping contest :D

 The main map will be later =))


showcase  time segment 55sec

Good luck =)

The concept of the map is a big closed chamber, in which the walls are being generated by chance. The player might either meet an enemy or pass him by. Buy zone is included, for CTs on the T spawn and vice versa. The map objective is to eliminate the enemy team.
Short map for beginners.

(Sorry for bad English)

How to Install:
1. Open your steamapps folder. (Default is "C:\Program
Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\counter-strike source")
2.Open "cstrike\maps\"
3.Copy dust2background.bsp to this folder
4.Open "cstrike\cfg\"
5.Copy autoexec.cfg to this folder

_aLatestUpdates._sText:
Correction with the bots' passage area has been made. 

In particular, the texture of the npc_clip has been removed, which prevents the ct bots from passing to the right side of the map on the respawn.

An error correction was also implemented, causing a glitch in the form of white lines in the sky.

de_akihabara is a port of the de_akihabara from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

Akihabara:
A bomb defusal map set in a centre of Tokyo's Shopping district named Akihabara!

During routine road-maintenance an unexploded World War 2 bomb is exposed, causing fears that a segment of Akihabara could be destroyed if the situation is not resolved by police forces!

Terrorists have leapt on the opportunity to create chaos in the city district and are planning on setting it off!

_aLatestUpdates._sText:
bhop_hextra-f brings the course to its polished/final state - major reworking of the stage flow+interactions, obstacles reduced to make speedruns more feasible. 

the bonus takes away all bhop platforms, making the stage floors solid. there is a green hexagon near the middle - surf up to it for a 600u boost each pass! a total of 6 boosts possible in the bonus run, however the first may be tricky to reach!

_sText:
bhop_hextra is a hexagonal tunnel with bhops on all sides.
the structure repeats itself to create 6 stages, only rolled 60 degrees per copy.
bhops then double as surf ramps and ledges, useful for speed+height in adjacent stages!

this map started as a small concept map bhop_cubic_a1 - and many many years of struggling with blender, finally I'm satisfied with how this came out. special thanks for all that gave feedback on v1, truly hope that more will enjoy this version of the map!

dod_jagdy is a port with cuted of the official dod_jagd map from Day of Defeat: Source game.
